    "For most of the local learning algorithms, this output was a set of local structures such as Markov Blankets, rather than a whole integrated graph.",
    "However, when these algorithms have subsequently been incorporated into software packages, for example, Inter-IAMB in the bnlearn software package (Scutari 2021) these local structures may be merged, and the output would then be a whole graph, typically a CPDAG.",
